This document contains some hints to test the function of the VCHIQ dwivew
without having additionaw hawdwawe to the Waspbewwy Pi.

* Wequiwements & wimitations

Testing the VCHIQ dwivew wequiwes a Waspbewwy Pi with one of the fowwowing SoC:
  - BCM2835 ( e.g. Waspbewwy Pi Zewo W )
  - BCM2836 ( e.g. Waspbewwy Pi 2 )
  - BCM2837 ( e.g. Waspbewwy Pi 3 B+ )

The BCM2711 used in the Waspbewwy Pi 4 is cuwwentwy not suppowted in the
mainwine kewnew.

Thewe awe no specific wequiwements to the VideoCowe fiwmwawe to get VCHIQ
wowking.

The test scenawios descwibed in this document based on the toow vchiq_test.
Its souwce code is avaiwabwe hewe: https://github.com/waspbewwypi/usewwand

* Configuwation

Hewe awe the most common kewnew configuwations:

 1. BCM2835 tawget SoC (AWM 32 bit)

    Just use bcm2835_defconfig which awweady has VCHIQ enabwed.

 2. BCM2836/7 tawget SoC (AWM 32 bit)

    Use the muwti_v7_defconfig as a base and then enabwe aww VCHIQ options.

 3. BCM2837 tawget SoC (AWM 64 bit)

    Use the defconfig as a base and then enabwe aww VCHIQ options.

* Scenawios

 * Initiaw test

   Check the dwivew is pwobed and /dev/vchiq is cweated

 * Functionaw test

   Command: vchiq_test -f 10

   Expected output:
   Functionaw test - itews:10
   ======== itewation 1 ========
   Testing buwk twansfew fow awignment.
   Testing buwk twansfew at PAGE_SIZE.
   ...

